    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《圣物深渊》是一款充满动作、融合了洛夫克拉夫特式幻想与中世纪科幻，并配有可爱艺术风格和精彩配乐的的另类游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/21f5b9f28134d6807e9d7822c337d605.poster.avif?t=1770712921\" width=780 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/21f5b9f28134d6807e9d7822c337d605.webm?t=1770712921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/21f5b9f28134d6807e9d7822c337d605.mp4?t=1770712921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索正被深渊吞噬、荒凉而美丽的世界。踏上生存的旅程，一路上结识其他冒险家！发现古代圣物，锻造强大的装备，发展您的技能来击败原始邪恶并防止灾难！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧙‍​​♀️遊玩多達 20 位獨特設計的冒險家</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/48c55cd93831866ce1ce76b1a7f8d311.avif?t=1770712921\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🔥超过 134 种独特的角色技能，包括终极技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/7f48f4a73de5518e825d987ee70f6a05.avif?t=1770712921\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💪选择您自己的搭配方式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/c23b8d3c809bbfc89348cc1f48d08bc8.avif?t=1770712921\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚒️升级您的装备</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/37612c61eef264e84ede92a43f065dd9.avif?t=1770712921\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🃏收集集敌人卡片及镶嵌您的装备</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/12ddbfe96c9798825abb4c6971296333.avif?t=1770712921\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👑发现强大的圣物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/6d930ff7d50d111ce1a41dc94ffb9eba.poster.avif?t=1770712921\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/6d930ff7d50d111ce1a41dc94ffb9eba.webm?t=1770712921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗺️循序生成的关卡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/51b603c8d8eeff80ff4f1b97828af34e.poster.avif?t=1770712921\" width=780 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/51b603c8d8eeff80ff4f1b97828af34e.webm?t=1770712921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨隨機化加成系統</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/0ae09c830cd17f7bc9d8f41f5fe6d986.avif?t=1770712921\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦑与异世界头目战斗</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/90e04a79b17a29db08dcc1af14839778.poster.avif?t=1770712921\" width=780 height=532 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/90e04a79b17a29db08dcc1af14839778.webm?t=1770712921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/90e04a79b17a29db08dcc1af14839778.mp4?t=1770712921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏙️扩充根据地等级中的城市建设元素</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/f1d61c9f3f122267249c5623720fd0c0.avif?t=1770712921\" width=800 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧓透過訓練提升您的能力</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/894d8f367aca7aaec77df7a4d0c59927.avif?t=1770712921\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🪜 6 个包含独特遭遇的可玩关卡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/6742c41e7b911d1cbc12c7af250fd137.avif?t=1770712921\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👺难度按等级递增</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/d540c74f796d2957f9ac17909abc2154.avif?t=1770712921\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >原配乐：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏也配有超过 1 小时 40 分钟的配乐。 每个关卡都会播放 5 首独特配乐。 全部由 Buch Dacanay 热情创作！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >配乐主题曲为《正面抑郁》。 这跟游戏故事情节中探索的主题完美匹配。</p>",
